{"meta":{"version":"121","folder":"EventFlowMsg","file":"DmT_ZE_Molduga","chunk":0,"start":0,"count":23,"total":23},"rows":[{"id":10794,"index":0,"key":"DmT_ZE_Molduga_Text_000_abb","CNzh":"海拉鲁王国将落入我手……","TWzh":"我要將海拉魯王國納為己有……","JPja":"ハイラル<Ruby={4:8}おうこく>王国を<Ruby={2:2}わ>我が<Ruby={2:2}て>手に…","USen":"Hyrule will bow down before me."},{"id":10795,"index":1,"key":"DmT_ZE_Molduga_Text_000_ac","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10796,"index":2,"key":"DmT_ZE_Molduga_Text_000_b","CNzh":"一大群莫尔德拉吉克正在接近！","TWzh":"有一群莫爾德拉吉克正在接近我們！","JPja":"モルドラジークの<Ruby={2:2}む>群れが<Ruby={6:14}せっきんちゅう>接近中！","USen":"Molduga are approaching our position!"},{"id":10797,"index":3,"key":"DmT_ZE_Molduga_Text_001_b","CNzh":"总数不明！\n总、总之数量极多！！","TWzh":"總數不明！\n數……數量十分龐大！！","JPja":"<Ruby={8:14}そうすうふめい>総数不明！\nも…もの<Ruby={2:4}すご>凄い<Ruby={2:4}かず>数です！！","USen":"It's more than we thought! It's a swarm!"},{"id":10798,"index":4,"key":"DmT_ZE_Molduga_Text_002_bb","CNzh":"居然会有那么多莫尔德拉吉克！\n究竟发生了什么……","TWzh":"居然有這麼多莫爾德拉吉克！\n究竟發生了什麼事……","JPja":"モルドラジークがあんなに！\nいったい どうして…","USen":"There are so many of them! But why would they..."},{"id":10799,"index":5,"key":"DmT_ZE_Molduga_Text_002_d","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10800,"index":6,"key":"DmT_ZE_Molduga_Text_003_b","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10801,"index":7,"key":"DmT_ZE_Molduga_Text_003_bc","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10802,"index":8,"key":"DmT_ZE_Molduga_Text_003_d","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10803,"index":9,"key":"DmT_ZE_Molduga_Text_004_aab","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10804,"index":10,"key":"DmT_ZE_Molduga_Text_004_ac","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10805,"index":11,"key":"DmT_ZE_Molduga_Text_004_b","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10806,"index":12,"key":"DmT_ZE_Molduga_Text_005_c","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10807,"index":13,"key":"DmT_ZE_Molduga_Text_006_ab","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10808,"in